<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 18:12:13 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>世界银行预测2024年全球经济增长将连续第三年放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/world-bank-forecasts-2024-global-growth-slow-third-consecutive-year-2024-01-09/</link><description>世界银行周二警告称，2024年全球经济增长将连续第三年放缓，许多发展中国家的贫困现象将长期存在，债务水平将进一步恶化。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 14:35:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/world-bank-forecasts-2024-global-growth-slow-third-consecutive-year-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>由于进口下降，美国 11 月贸易逆差缩小</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-trade-deficit-narrows-november-imports-fall-2024-01-09/</link><description>由于国内需求放缓，消费品进口跌至一年来新低，美国11月贸易逆差意外收窄，如果这一趋势持续到12月，贸易可能不会对第四季度经济增长产生影响。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 13:47:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-trade-deficit-narrows-november-imports-fall-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>哥谭市报告后，格里福斯将于周二下午召开董事会会议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/grifols-hold-board-meeting-tuesday-afternoon-after-gotham-city-report-2024-01-09/</link><description>西班牙制药公司 Grifols 董事会成员托马斯·达加 (Tomas Daga) 告诉路透社，该公司定于周二下午召开董事会会议，以回应 Gotham City Research 质疑该公司早些时候发布的会计报告的报告。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 11:24:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/grifols-hold-board-meeting-tuesday-afternoon-after-gotham-city-report-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国集团：2023年中国可能取代日本成为全球最大汽车出口国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-likely-dethroned-japan-worlds-top-auto-exporter-2023-china-group-2024-01-09/</link><description>中国乘用车协会(CPCA)周二表示，随着比亚迪、奇瑞等国内汽车制造商在海外取得重大进展，中国预计将在2023年超过日本成为全球最大的汽车出口国。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 11:11:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-likely-dethroned-japan-worlds-top-auto-exporter-2023-china-group-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：华尔街重新找到魔力 - 但前方仍存在障碍</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-01-09/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 11:07:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>英国牛津纳米孔公司（Oxford Nanopore）营收预警后股价下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/britains-oxford-nanopores-shares-sink-after-revenue-warning-2024-01-09/</link><description>英国牛津纳米孔公司(Oxford Nanopore)周二发布收入预警，称其股价下跌近12%，原因是中国和中东经济放缓，以及大客户的交错采购。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 11:01:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/britains-oxford-nanopores-shares-sink-after-revenue-warning-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国汽车品牌通过电动汽车升级提高盈利能力-瑞银</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-auto-brands-improve-profitability-with-ev-upgrades-ubs-2024-01-09/</link><description>瑞银分析师周二表示，尽管全球最大汽车市场的竞争加剧，但由于中国汽车品牌不断升级电动汽车（EV）产品组合，中国汽车品牌预计将在 2024 年实现更好的盈利能力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 09:57:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-auto-brands-improve-profitability-with-ev-upgrades-ubs-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国卫星发射在关键投票前引发台湾攻击警报</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-alert-says-chinese-satellite-flies-over-south-taiwan-airspace-2024-01-09/</link><description>台湾政府周二发布空袭警报，称一枚携带卫星的中国火箭飞越台湾南部领空，台湾外交部长称这是关键选举前几天骚扰行为的一部分。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 07:50:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-alert-says-chinese-satellite-flies-over-south-taiwan-airspace-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>哥谭市会计查询使 Grifols 价值损失 38.3 亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/short-seller-gotham-city-questions-grifols-debt-ratios-2024-01-09/</link><description>在对冲基金 Gotham City Research 对其会计提出质疑后，Grifols 股价周二下跌 30%，市值蒸发近 30 亿美元，促使这家西班牙制药商“断然”否认有任何不当行为。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 07:22:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/short-seller-gotham-city-questions-grifols-debt-ratios-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>桥梁困境凸显台湾选举中对中国的分歧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/bridge-dilemma-captures-divide-over-china-taiwan-elections-2024-01-09/</link><description>陈沧江指着办公室一水之隔的厦门摩天大楼，回忆起30年前这座中国南方城市和台湾金门岛一样低矮的情况。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 07:18:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/bridge-dilemma-captures-divide-over-china-taiwan-elections-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>印尼准备与各国合作敲定南海法规</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-ready-work-with-countries-finalise-south-china-sea-code-2024-01-09/</link><description>印度尼西亚外交部长蕾特诺·马尔苏迪周二表示，印度尼西亚准备与其他东南亚国家合作，敲定拖延已久的南海行为准则，该国许多邻国与中国在南海存在重叠的主权声索。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 06:55:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-ready-work-with-countries-finalise-south-china-sea-code-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>经济疲软、新冠疫情肆虐可能导致2023年中国人口再次减少</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/weak-economy-covid-rampage-likely-shrank-chinas-population-again-2023-2024-01-09/</link><description>由于中国突然结束严格的封锁，与新冠病毒相关的死亡人数激增，2023年中国人口可能连续第二年下降，而对经济前景的信心疲弱导致出生率低迷。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 06:03:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/weak-economy-covid-rampage-likely-shrank-chinas-population-again-2023-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>随着印度关系恶化，马尔代夫总统吸引中国投资者</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/maldives-president-courts-investors-china-ties-with-india-sag-2024-01-09/</link><description>在中国南部港口城市举行的“投资马尔代夫”论坛上，马尔代夫总统穆罕默德·穆伊祖与面带微笑的当地官员握手并交换了意见，此次访问中国旨在深化双边关系，因为这个群岛国家正在远离印度。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 05:52:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/maldives-president-courts-investors-china-ties-with-india-sag-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车巨头比亚迪将于下周在印度尼西亚推出汽车 - 公司</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-giant-byd-launch-cars-indonesia-next-week-company-2024-01-09/</link><description>中国比亚迪公司周二表示，该公司是全球最大的纯电动汽车（BEV）销售商，该公司将于下周在印度尼西亚推出其汽车。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 05:28:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-giant-byd-launch-cars-indonesia-next-week-company-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>香港领导人表示国泰航空需要解决运力问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/cathay-pacific-needs-address-capacity-issues-hong-kong-leader-says-2024-01-09/</link><description>香港领导人表示，香港国泰航空计划在繁忙的农历新年期间削减航班，这表明该航空公司需要解决运力问题，而其飞行员工会则呼吁政府进行调查。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 04:22:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/cathay-pacific-needs-address-capacity-issues-hong-kong-leader-says-2024-01-09/</guid></item></channel></rss>